Key Match Events: Jalen Williams scored 23 points, Shai Gilgeous-Alexander added 21 points and nine assists, and the Oklahoma City Thunder defeated the Orlando Magic 102-86
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Thunder have won all seven of its games by at least 12 points
Others: Isaiah Joe scored 13 points, Aaron Wiggins had 11 points, Chet Holmgren added 14 points, nine rebounds and two blocks for the Thunder. Orlando (3-5) played without injured starters Paolo Banchero and Wendell Carter Jr.
